### ============================================
### 어드민 API 테스트 (REST Client for VS Code)
### ============================================
### 사용법:
### 1. VS Code 확장 "REST Client" 설치
### 2. 서버 실행: npm run start:dev
### 3. 각 요청 위의 "Send Request" 클릭
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@adminToken = {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
@categoryId = {{createCategory.response.body.id}}
@policyId = {{createPolicy.response.body.id}}
@levelId = {{createLevel.response.body.id}}

### ============================================
### 1. 인증 (Authentication)
### ============================================

### 1-1. OAuth 로그인 (구글) - 브라우저에서 직접 접근
# GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/google

### 1-2. 어드민 비밀번호 설정 (OAuth 로그인 후 토큰 필요)
### 먼저 OAuth 로그인 후 받은 토큰을 아래에 입력하세요
# @name setPassword
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/admin/set-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_OAUTH_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### 1-3. 어드민 이메일/비밀번호 로그인
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### 1-4. 어드민 비밀번호 변경
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/auth/admin/change-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "currentPassword": "Admin123!",
  "newPassword": "NewAdmin456!"
}

### ============================================
### 2. 유저 관리 (User Management)
### ============================================

### 2-1. 유저 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2-2. 유저 권한 변경 (어드민 권한 부여)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/USER_ID_HERE/role
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "type": "admin"
}

### 2-3. 유저 권한 변경 (일반 유저로 변경)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/USER_ID_HERE/role
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "type": "member"
}

### ============================================
### 3. 게시판 카테고리 (Board Categories)
### ============================================

### 3-1. 카테고리 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/boards/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3-2. 카테고리 생성
# @name createCategory
POST {{baseUrl}}/boards/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "label": "자유게시판"
}

### 3-3. 카테고리 수정
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/boards/categories/{{categoryId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "label": "질문게시판",
  "status": "enabled"
}

### 3-4. 카테고리 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/boards/categories/{{categoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 4. 포인트 정책 (Point Policies)
### ============================================

### 4-1. 포인트 정책 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/points/policies
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4-2. 포인트 정책 생성 (영상 시청)
# @name createPolicy
POST {{baseUrl}}/points/policies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "actionType": "WATCH",
  "pointAmount": 100,
  "isOneTime": false,
  "isActive": true
}

### 4-3. 포인트 정책 생성 (챌린지 완료)
POST {{baseUrl}}/points/policies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "actionType": "CHALLENGE",
  "pointAmount": 500,
  "isOneTime": true,
  "isActive": true
}

### 4-4. 포인트 정책 생성 (댓글 작성)
POST {{baseUrl}}/points/policies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "actionType": "COMMENT",
  "pointAmount": 50,
  "isOneTime": false,
  "isActive": true
}

### 4-5. 포인트 정책 수정
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/points/policies/{{policyId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "pointAmount": 150,
  "isActive": true
}

### 4-6. 포인트 정책 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/points/policies/{{policyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 5. XP 레벨 정책 (XP Level Policies)
### ============================================

### 5-1. XP 레벨 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/xp/levels
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 5-2. XP 레벨 생성 (레벨 1)
# @name createLevel
POST {{baseUrl}}/xp/levels
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "level": 1,
  "minXp": 0,
  "maxXp": 99,
  "label": "입문자"
}

### 5-3. XP 레벨 생성 (레벨 2)
POST {{baseUrl}}/xp/levels
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "level": 2,
  "minXp": 100,
  "maxXp": 299,
  "label": "초보자"
}

### 5-4. XP 레벨 생성 (레벨 3)
POST {{baseUrl}}/xp/levels
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "level": 3,
  "minXp": 300,
  "maxXp": 599,
  "label": "중급자"
}

### 5-5. XP 레벨 수정
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/xp/levels/{{levelId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "label": "뜨개 입문자",
  "maxXp": 149
}

### 5-6. XP 레벨 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/xp/levels/{{levelId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 6. 채널 관리 (Channel Management)
### ============================================

### 6-1. 채널 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/channels
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6-2. 채널 등록
# @name createChannel
POST {{baseUrl}}/channels
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "뜨개질 마스터",
  "youtubeChannelId": "UC1234567890abcdef"
}

### 6-3. 채널 수정
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/channels/CHANNEL_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "뜨개질 전문가"
}

### 6-4. 채널 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/channels/CHANNEL_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 7. 콘텐츠 관리 (Content Management)
### ============================================

### 7-1. 콘텐츠 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/contents?interests=crochet
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7-2. 콘텐츠 등록
POST {{baseUrl}}/contents
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "channelId": "CHANNEL_ID_HERE",
  "youtubeVideoId": "dQw4w9WgXcQ",
  "name": "기초 코바늘 강좌 1편",
  "type": "symbol",
  "interests": "crochet",
  "pointApplyable": true
}

### 7-3. 콘텐츠 순서 변경
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/contents/CONTENT_ID_HERE/order
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "previousContentId": null,
  "nextContentId": "NEXT_CONTENT_ID_HERE"
}

### 7-4. 콘텐츠 수정
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/contents/CONTENT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "기초 코바늘 강좌 1편 (수정됨)",
  "pointApplyable": false
}

### 7-5. 콘텐츠 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/contents/CONTENT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 8. 포인트/XP 지급 (Admin Grant)
### ============================================

### 8-1. 포인트 지급
POST {{baseUrl}}/points/earn
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "memberId": "USER_ID_HERE",
  "actionType": "WATCH",
  "referenceId": "CONTENT_ID_HERE"
}

### 8-2. XP 지급
POST {{baseUrl}}/xp/earn
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "memberId": "USER_ID_HERE",
  "amount": 50,
  "reason": "이벤트 보상"
}
